00:04:03.220 --> 00:04:06.600
"Summer"

00:04:03.380 --> 00:04:08.010
but sometimes I feel like there's
this gaping hole in my chest...

00:04:08.010 --> 00:04:10.980
You're personifying summer now?

00:04:10.980 --> 00:04:13.850
I guess you get hyped for it, too.

00:04:13.850 --> 00:04:16.360
