She's gone beyond shameless.

00:16:30.090 --> 00:16:33.640
Of course you could!
Why, I've had my eye on you!

00:16:33.640 --> 00:16:35.890
Is she confessing her crush or what?

00:16:35.890 --> 00:16:39.310
I-If you don't like frills,
we can--I--oh--wh-white!

00:16:39.310 --> 00:16:41.810
Yes, a plain white T-shirt would be fine!

00:16:41.810 --> 00:16:45.940
Over a swimsuit! No! Forget the swimsuit!

00:16:45.940 --> 00:16:48.190
You'd wear a white T-shirt, wouldn't you?!

00:16:48.190 --> 00:16:51.280
And I'll put kind of a high stage
in the middle of the café,

00:16:51.280 --> 00:16:53.450
and I'll have you two stand on that!

00:16:53.450 --> 00:16:54.990
--Uh-huh, uh-huh.
--And then!

00:16:54.990 --> 00:16:56.700
And then?

00:16:56.700 --> 00:16:58.410
I'll use this squirt gun, see?

00:16:58.410 --> 00:16:59.830
A squirt gun--yes?

00:17:19.310 --> 00:17:23.020
Why the outfit, Ami?

00:17:23.020 --> 00:17:27.940
I-I've been thinking about
the future of this café...

00:17:27.940 --> 00:17:31.360
I guess she's not big on wearing
an embarrassing outfit herself.

00:17:31.360 --> 00:17:33.740
You're staring, Senpai.

00:17:33.740 --> 00:17:35.860
I am not either!

00:17:40.870 --> 00:17:43.410
You can't fall asleep yet, Senpai!

00:17:43.410 --> 00:17:46.580
One more round! One more!

00:17:46.580 --> 00:17:49.670
You want to quit now--as a <i>loser</i>?

00:17:48.920 --> 00:17:51.670
"Senpai"

00:17:49.670 --> 00:17:51.880
Look, it's two in the morning.

00:17:51.880 --> 00:17:55.090
Just one more round--that's all!

00:17:55.090 --> 00:17:56.430
Are you listening?

00:17:56.430 --> 00:17:58.140
Hey! Senpai!

00:17:57.140 --> 00:18:01.100
"Senpai"

00:17:59.800 --> 00:18:01.760
Hey! Did you fall asleep?!

00:18:01.760 --> 00:18:04.020
I can't beat this guy
all by myself, y'know!

00:18:04.020 --> 00:18:04.980
Coward!

00:18:04.980 --> 00:18:06.770
Wake up, you chicken!

00:18:06.770 --> 00:18:09.770
Hana! Do you have
any idea what time it is?

00:18:09.770 --> 00:18:11.520
Hang on a sec, Mom!

00:18:11.520 --> 00:18:14.650
I'm gonna save, okay?
So hands off that plug--

00:18:14.650 --> 00:18:15.820
Yoink!

00:18:23.370 --> 00:18:25.160
You sure are sleepy today.

00:18:25.160 --> 00:18:28.330
It's Uzaki. These past few nights...

00:18:28.330 --> 00:18:31.250
I keep saying we should
go to sleep already,

00:18:31.250 --> 00:18:33.630
but she's all "One more round! One more!"

00:18:33.630 --> 00:18:35.880
I know what it <i>sounds</i> like,

00:18:35.880 --> 00:18:38.130
but they're up late playing games, right?

00:18:38.130 --> 00:18:40.140
Bet on it.

00:18:40.140 --> 00:18:42.390
Want to nap till second hour?

00:18:42.390 --> 00:18:43.930
I'll wake you up.

00:18:45.520 --> 00:18:46.680
Please.

00:18:46.680 --> 00:18:49.770
And that's when Ito's boyfriend...

00:18:49.770 --> 00:18:51.360
Whoa, seriously?

00:18:51.360 --> 00:18:54.820
C'mon, don't say it...

00:18:56.190 --> 00:18:58.990
Hey, Hana! We saved you a seat.

00:18:58.990 --> 00:19:00.990
Oh, thanks.

00:19:00.990 --> 00:19:03.280
The villain has landed.

00:19:03.280 --> 00:19:06.660
She hasn't seen you yet. Snooze away.

00:19:06.660 --> 00:19:09.920
But you <i>have</i> a boyfriend. I'm so jealous!

00:19:09.920 --> 00:19:13.800
Don't be. It's so tiring--a lot of work!

00:19:13.800 --> 00:19:16.880
It sounds like bragging when
you say it with a face like that!

00:19:16.880 --> 00:19:20.340
Boyfriends, ha! What a hassle.

00:19:20.340 --> 00:19:24.510
But <i>you</i> have one, too, don't you?

00:19:24.510 --> 00:19:27.100
You know: You're always
going home together.

00:19:27.100 --> 00:19:29.440
Tall guy--kind of scary.

00:19:29.440 --> 00:19:33.610
I've seen you be really
friendly together, tons of times.

00:19:33.610 --> 00:19:37.860
See? I <i>told</i> you that's
how you two come across.

00:19:37.860 --> 00:19:39.530
Lucky him.

00:19:39.530 --> 00:19:42.820
With all this girl talk,
Uzaki might let her true feelings slip.

00:19:42.820 --> 00:19:46.120
Oh, him? He's not like that.

00:19:46.120 --> 00:19:48.580
I just hang out with him--as a favor.

00:19:50.210 --> 00:19:52.460
A-As a favor?

00:19:52.460 --> 00:19:54.630
I mean, he is <i>so</i> gloomy!

00:19:54.630 --> 00:19:57.880
Not a lot of friends, always on his own...

00:19:57.880 --> 00:20:00.760
But I can't let that go--he
was my high-school senpai.

00:20:00.760 --> 00:20:03.090
I just <i>have</i> give him
some attention, poor thing!

00:20:03.090 --> 00:20:05.100
Is she serious?

00:20:05.100 --> 00:20:07.890
So actually, I have no choice.

00:20:07.890 --> 00:20:09.020
Really?

00:20:09.020 --> 00:20:12.150
Yeah, really. He's a handful!

00:20:12.150 --> 00:20:14.610
Oh, he's hearing this. For sure.

00:20:18.820 --> 00:20:22.910
Honestly. Just saying
whatever works for her...

00:20:22.910 --> 00:20:24.240
Damn.

00:20:25.370 --> 00:20:28.120
My sleepiness came back
after eating lunch.

00:20:28.120 --> 00:20:31.120
I never did get any
sleep during all that...

00:20:31.120 --> 00:20:33.960
I'm just going to
sleep off my indignation.

00:20:40.300 --> 00:20:41.930
I <i>knew</i> you were over here!

00:20:41.930 --> 00:20:43.430
Senpai, Senpai!

00:20:47.600 --> 00:20:50.770
Wow, you really can sleep anywhere, huh?

00:20:50.770 --> 00:20:54.770
That's a sloppy,
thick-skinned guy for you.

00:20:54.770 --> 00:20:58.440
I guess I've been keeping him up
late these past few days.

00:20:58.440 --> 00:21:02.780
Ah, well. We have fourth hour together;
I'll just wait here till he wakes up.

00:21:25.340 --> 00:21:28.300
Ha. Delete, delete...

00:21:37.310 --> 00:21:39.770
Is this where Hana's been--sleeping?

00:21:39.770 --> 00:21:42.110
Fourth hour is about to begin!

00:21:42.110 --> 00:21:44.990
Those two, I tell ya.

00:21:44.990 --> 00:21:48.120
No matter how much
they themselves deny it...

00:21:48.120 --> 00:21:51.450
That thing about them not dating?
It <i>had </i>to be a lie.

00:21:51.450 --> 00:21:53.250
Totally.

00:21:53.250 --> 00:21:56.420
...they're thoroughly unconvincing.

00:21:56.420 --> 00:22:00.420
Now, which one would be
funnier to wake up first?

00:23:35.470 --> 00:23:39.980
"Next Time"
"Episode 2: I Want to Make
Udon After We Hang Out!"
